text.div:
This value set includes codes based on the following rules:

  • Import all the codes that are contained in TNM Regional Nodes Category Value Set
  • Include all codes defined in https://www.uicc.org/resources/tnm

name: TNMRegionalNodesCategoryMaxVS

description: Values for TNM regional nodes category must be selected from this value set, which includes all codes from UICC and all codes from TNMRegionalNodesCategoryVS.
